title: World Cup qualifiers: India lose five in a row as Oman cruise to 3-0 victory
text:
*Muscat:* Indian football team's abject humilation continued as they slumped to their fifth consecutive defeat in the 2018 FIFA World Cup qualifying round, losing 0-3 to Oman in an away game here yesterday.
*Oman's Eid al-Farsi (in red) is tackled by India's Bikash Jairu*
